name: Julie Hamilton
text: My first visit to Papa Murphy's was a good experience. Their Pizza is Top Notch compared to other pizza places. You just take and bake.  I'll be a regular there.

name: Lauren Reese
text: Sign up for text coupons and you can get a really great deal. All large pizzas are $10 on Tuesday. Search Google for Papa Murphy's hacks and you'll find all the tricks for how to get the best out of your pizza

name: Logan Van Hoose
text: We love it and you can always add additional toppings yourself at home if you want.  The prices are super affordable.
